html.textContent:
Table Vertical Alignment Test
  
    body { margin: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    table { border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0; }
    th, td { padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #666; background: #fff; height: 60px; }
    thead th { background: #f0f0f0; }
    caption { caption-side: top; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .top { vertical-align: top; }
    .middle { vertical-align: middle; }
    .bottom { vertical-align: bottom; }
    .baseline { vertical-align: baseline; }
  


  
    Vertical Alignment Test (60px cell height)
    
      
        Alignment
        Content
        Description
      
    
    
      
        Top
        This content should be aligned to the top of the cell
        Default alignment
      
      
        Middle
        This content should be centered vertically in the cell
        Centered alignment
      
      
        Bottom
        This content should be aligned to the bottom of the cell
        Bottom alignment
      
      
        Baseline
        This content should align to text baseline
        Baseline alignment
      
      
        Multi-rowMiddle
        Top in multi-row context
        Bottom in multi-row context
      
      
        Middle in multi-row context
        Baseline in multi-row context
